WEBVTT

01:40.380 --> 01:48.740
[You are My Fateful Love]
[EP02]

01:49.860 --> 01:50.619
Here, Miss Ruan.

01:51.459 --> 01:51.979
Come on in.

01:51.979 --> 01:52.419
Thanks.

02:18.979 --> 02:19.620
Mr. Liu.

02:19.859 --> 02:20.460
I got it.

02:20.819 --> 02:21.859
No problem. It's nothing.

02:31.180 --> 02:31.900
Let me. Thanks.

02:51.139 --> 02:51.979
You two know each other?

02:57.660 --> 02:58.900
No. No, we don't.

03:08.660 --> 03:09.220
No.

03:13.100 --> 03:13.979
Let me introduce you then.

03:14.539 --> 03:14.979
This is

03:14.979 --> 03:15.979
our firm's legal counsel,

03:15.979 --> 03:16.419
Xu Huaisong.

03:26.060 --> 03:26.579
Hello.

03:31.139 --> 03:31.579
And this

03:31.579 --> 03:32.859
is our client for this case.

03:33.259 --> 03:33.859
Ruan Yu.

03:34.979 --> 03:35.699
Miss Ruan.

03:37.220 --> 03:38.139
A novelist.

03:38.739 --> 03:39.979
Specializes in romance.

03:43.780 --> 03:46.699
Mr. Xu, how'd you know that?

03:47.340 --> 03:48.699
I looked over your file.

03:57.780 --> 04:00.660
And how much do you know?

04:03.259 --> 04:06.100
About the case? Or about the person?

04:08.180 --> 04:09.460
Or maybe your novel?

04:14.539 --> 04:16.259
Mr. Xu just means

04:16.539 --> 04:17.139
we'd like to

04:17.139 --> 04:18.299
get some basic info

04:18.620 --> 04:19.819
on our clients before the discussion.

04:19.819 --> 04:20.340
It's part

04:20.340 --> 04:21.819
of being

04:22.259 --> 04:22.859
a good lawyer,

04:23.139 --> 04:23.660
right?

04:24.539 --> 04:25.619
Got the basics covered.

04:26.220 --> 04:27.539
Haven't read the novel yet, right?

04:28.939 --> 04:29.660
Oh right, Miss Ruan,

04:29.939 --> 04:31.059
you brought the novel, yeah?

04:38.140 --> 04:38.820
I... Yeah.

04:39.340 --> 04:39.939
Good.

04:39.939 --> 04:41.059
Just hand it to Mr. Xu

04:41.059 --> 04:41.580
later.

04:42.059 --> 04:42.660
Have a seat.

04:43.780 --> 04:44.140
Here.

04:50.979 --> 04:52.140
[This novel is basically]

04:52.820 --> 04:54.820
[a full-on fantasy]

04:55.539 --> 04:57.900
[about Xu Huaisong,]

04:57.900 --> 04:59.179
[from his body to his soul.]

05:00.539 --> 05:02.179
[And now I have to]

05:02.859 --> 05:04.499
[give it to him,]

05:05.499 --> 05:07.299
[and then dive]

05:07.979 --> 05:09.059
[into a legal discussion]

05:09.619 --> 05:11.499
[about the fantasy]

05:11.939 --> 05:13.539
[with him?]

05:16.539 --> 05:17.419
Gentlemen,

05:17.499 --> 05:18.220
as they say,

05:18.220 --> 05:19.379
let mercy guide your hand.

05:19.379 --> 05:20.260
Patience brings peace.

05:20.260 --> 05:21.260
A step back gives room to breathe.

05:21.619 --> 05:23.499
Saving a life is the greatest virtue.

05:27.379 --> 05:28.660
Miss Ruan, what do you mean?

05:29.539 --> 05:30.979
I... I mean,

05:31.780 --> 05:33.020
I suddenly don't wanna sue anymore.

05:34.419 --> 05:35.220
Don't wanna sue?

05:41.260 --> 05:42.260
Are you... sure about that?

05:48.539 --> 05:49.179
Just a sec.

05:49.179 --> 05:49.979
I gotta take this.

05:49.979 --> 05:50.700
Sorry.

05:57.220 --> 05:57.660
Hello?

05:59.260 --> 05:59.900
What kind of delivery

05:59.900 --> 06:00.939
needs my signature in person?

06:02.780 --> 06:03.379
Okay. Coming.

06:07.900 --> 06:08.939
She suddenly doesn't wanna sue?

06:12.299 --> 06:13.260
Did I do something wrong?

06:24.660 --> 06:26.580
Mr. Liu's pretty busy, huh?

06:27.260 --> 06:28.179
Last time I saw him,

06:29.059 --> 06:30.660
he also had to step out

06:30.660 --> 06:31.539
for a call.

06:35.780 --> 06:36.460
Last time?

06:44.340 --> 06:44.859
Please.

08:06.179 --> 08:08.859
[He barely changed.]

08:10.419 --> 08:13.900
[Time's been way too kind to him.]

08:22.100 --> 08:22.780
Miss Ruan,

08:22.780 --> 08:23.619
you got a problem with me?

08:26.700 --> 08:27.340
No, no.

08:28.140 --> 08:28.820
Wouldn't dare.

08:29.780 --> 08:30.700
Just

08:31.100 --> 08:32.539
feeling sorry for myself.

09:26.139 --> 09:27.019
What's up, Mr. Xu?

09:32.060 --> 09:32.619
Sorry.

09:32.700 --> 09:33.379
Had to go downstairs

09:33.379 --> 09:34.460
to sign for a package.

09:37.139 --> 09:37.940
So, Miss Ruan,

09:37.940 --> 09:39.180
have you made up your mind?

09:39.460 --> 09:40.899
Mr. Liu, I've thought it through.

09:42.580 --> 09:42.940
Alright.

09:43.300 --> 09:44.340
I respect your decision.

09:45.220 --> 09:46.580
I've had plenty of clients

09:46.580 --> 09:48.300
who hesitate at the last minute.

09:49.300 --> 09:50.379
But after thinking it over,

09:50.700 --> 09:52.340
they usually go through with the lawsuit.

09:52.899 --> 09:54.100
It's fine. Take your time.

09:55.859 --> 09:56.820
Mr. Liu, you're talking

09:56.820 --> 09:58.139
about your divorce clients, right?

09:59.580 --> 10:01.300
Those two don't get along?

10:05.700 --> 10:06.460
Thanks, Mr. Liu.

10:07.739 --> 10:08.940
I'll think about it some more.

10:09.259 --> 10:11.100
Sure. Let me walk you out.

10:12.300 --> 10:12.739
Don't bother.

10:13.499 --> 10:14.180
Go ahead with your work.

10:14.580 --> 10:15.940
Running back and forth now

10:15.940 --> 10:16.700
will make you late for lunch.

10:16.979 --> 10:17.820
I'm not busy.

10:18.259 --> 10:20.100
I was just about to invite you to lunch.

10:21.420 --> 10:22.460
Then let me treat you.

10:22.739 --> 10:23.379
It's too much trouble for you.

10:23.619 --> 10:24.100
Alright.

10:25.259 --> 10:25.820
Western food?

10:27.180 --> 10:27.899
There is a Western restaurant

10:27.899 --> 10:28.899
near where she lived.

10:29.139 --> 10:29.460
Sure.

10:39.580 --> 10:41.300
So you two already made plans for lunch?

10:45.139 --> 10:45.739
I forgot about that.

10:47.460 --> 10:48.379
How about next time?

10:50.180 --> 10:52.540
But he's already gone downstairs.

10:56.100 --> 10:57.499
It's okay. I'll go tell him.

10:57.940 --> 10:58.379
Let's go.

11:13.779 --> 11:14.580
Wait for me upstairs.

11:14.979 --> 11:16.659
I'll drop Ruan Yu off

11:16.820 --> 11:18.220
and come back to eat with you, okay?

11:20.139 --> 11:20.859
There's a bed upstairs.

11:25.420 --> 11:27.180
You're gonna crash and fix

11:27.180 --> 11:27.859
your jet lag now?

11:30.659 --> 11:31.220
Let's go.

11:32.779 --> 11:33.300
Mr. Liu,

11:33.300 --> 11:34.340
I left your keys in the car.

11:34.460 --> 11:35.180
I'll head up then.

11:35.180 --> 11:35.739
Alright. Thanks.

11:39.899 --> 11:41.180
Then I'll drop Miss Ruan off first.

11:48.700 --> 11:49.019
Than...

11:53.340 --> 11:54.220
Thank you, Mr. Liu.

11:58.220 --> 11:58.820
No problem, Ruan Yu.

11:58.820 --> 11:59.619
You take the back.

11:59.619 --> 12:00.540
More comfortable back there.

12:03.659 --> 12:04.499
Thanks, Mr. Liu.

12:12.340 --> 12:13.100
Close the door yourself.

12:30.300 --> 12:32.499
Mr. Liu, I'm not going home.

12:32.700 --> 12:33.940
Can you drop me at a friend's place?

12:36.700 --> 12:37.300
Sure.

12:39.259 --> 12:40.019
It's not out of the way.

12:40.300 --> 12:41.180
It's actually closer.

12:41.700 --> 12:42.700
No problem.

12:42.820 --> 12:44.100
Just send me the address.

12:44.619 --> 12:45.060
Okay.

13:19.540 --> 13:20.139
Miss Ruan.

13:20.820 --> 13:22.100
Mind telling me

13:22.100 --> 13:23.300
which friend you're going to?

13:24.979 --> 13:26.259
That's a little direct, don't you think?

13:27.899 --> 13:28.460
You ask her then.

13:33.060 --> 13:33.859
My editor's place.

13:37.060 --> 13:37.499
Got it.

13:39.820 --> 13:40.979
Going to your editor's?

13:48.180 --> 13:48.779
What's up?

13:49.700 --> 13:50.499
The case didn't go through?

13:51.940 --> 13:52.420
Mingying.

13:53.700 --> 13:54.379
Guess

13:54.379 --> 13:55.259
who I ran into today?

13:55.979 --> 13:56.859
Liu Mao...

13:58.659 --> 13:59.499
He confessed to you?

14:00.580 --> 14:01.619
It's Xu Huaisong.

14:02.619 --> 14:03.259
Mingying.

14:04.540 --> 14:05.460
I met

14:05.460 --> 14:06.300
the real Xu Huaisong.

14:13.019 --> 14:14.259
Something's off.

14:15.300 --> 14:17.659
It's perfectly normal for me to care

14:17.659 --> 14:19.300
about who I'm being set up with.

14:19.820 --> 14:20.580
Then why

14:20.940 --> 14:23.100
are you so worried about it?

14:25.420 --> 14:27.259
Gotta know where my client's going.

14:28.379 --> 14:29.259
Problem?

14:30.340 --> 14:31.859
She's already out there

14:31.859 --> 14:32.779
looking for a boyfriend.

14:33.540 --> 14:34.259
Where else would she go?

14:34.700 --> 14:36.580
Just some regular friend's place.

14:37.619 --> 14:38.340
Easy for you

14:38.340 --> 14:39.340
to say now.

14:40.060 --> 14:41.139
What if she only went on the blind date

14:41.139 --> 14:42.700
to get her family off her back?

14:43.019 --> 14:44.139
You think you know my date

14:44.139 --> 14:45.180
better than I do?

14:49.460 --> 14:51.060
That call at the office this morning

14:51.060 --> 14:51.940
was you,

14:51.940 --> 14:52.739
wasn't it?

14:53.499 --> 14:54.580
Setting me up to leave?

14:55.739 --> 14:57.739
You're a little slow on the uptake.

14:58.259 --> 14:59.420
How'd you even become a lawyer?

15:04.220 --> 15:05.499
Your ex-girlfriend?

15:11.100 --> 15:11.859
Well,

15:14.460 --> 15:15.420
it's complicated.

15:15.940 --> 15:18.220
What's more complicated

15:18.220 --> 15:19.460
than an ex?

15:21.619 --> 15:23.379
Don't you think debt and credit

15:23.379 --> 15:24.060
are more complicated?

15:26.019 --> 15:27.019
She owes you money?

15:31.300 --> 15:31.619
No.

15:32.060 --> 15:33.019
Then what's the deal between you two?

15:33.019 --> 15:33.540
Just say it.

15:33.540 --> 15:34.580
Spit it out.

15:34.580 --> 15:35.619
Chinese food or Western food?

15:36.259 --> 15:37.019
Fine, don't tell me.

15:38.940 --> 15:39.700
I'm good with anything.

15:39.700 --> 15:40.659
I'm not hungry. Up to you.

15:42.060 --> 15:43.139
When are you leaving this time?

15:44.460 --> 15:44.899
Tomorrow.

15:46.499 --> 15:47.420
You just got back yesterday

15:47.420 --> 15:48.259
and you're leaving tomorrow?

15:48.820 --> 15:50.300
My client's trial

15:50.300 --> 15:51.940
is in less than 48 hours.

15:52.060 --> 15:52.859
Think I should be in a hurry?

15:53.259 --> 15:53.859
Then why'd you

15:53.859 --> 15:55.220
even bother coming back now?

16:04.300 --> 16:05.499
What is

16:05.499 --> 16:08.019
more important than a trial?

16:10.540 --> 16:11.300
Excuse me.

16:13.739 --> 16:14.100
Hello?

16:14.779 --> 16:15.420
Huaisong.

16:16.060 --> 16:17.820
I think I messed up.

16:19.100 --> 16:20.739
I think I might've

16:20.739 --> 16:21.580
screwed Ruan Yu over.

16:27.139 --> 16:28.100
Who did you just say?

16:28.700 --> 16:29.979
Ruan Yu.

16:29.979 --> 16:30.899
You forgot?

16:42.060 --> 16:42.659
Take it easy.

16:43.540 --> 16:44.220
Just take your time.

16:45.619 --> 16:47.060
I don't know what to do.

16:48.859 --> 16:50.180
I'll send you a photo.

16:55.859 --> 16:56.420
Huaisong!

16:56.940 --> 16:58.139
Here's the document you needed.

17:02.180 --> 17:03.060
That night,

17:03.820 --> 17:05.420
I found this in the piano room

17:05.779 --> 17:06.700
at the school art gallery.

17:16.260 --> 17:18.020
You spend over ten hours flying back,

17:18.540 --> 17:19.179
stay for a day,

17:19.540 --> 17:21.260
then fly another ten-plus hours back.

17:22.139 --> 17:23.260
I think you've lost it.

17:25.859 --> 17:27.100
Who wouldn't?

17:29.619 --> 17:30.179
Crazy.

17:31.419 --> 17:32.699
I'm losing it.

17:34.219 --> 17:36.179
Who was it that swore up and down

17:36.419 --> 17:37.820
they wouldn't get caught?

17:39.260 --> 17:40.500
This is insane.

17:40.780 --> 17:41.820
I never thought it'd actually

17:41.820 --> 17:43.139
make its way to him.

17:44.179 --> 17:45.619
You wouldn't even see this in a novel.

17:47.379 --> 17:48.300
What do I do?

17:49.139 --> 17:50.219
I put out a post saying

17:50.219 --> 17:51.740
the novel was based on my real life,

17:52.260 --> 17:53.540
and also shared a video

17:53.540 --> 17:54.500
clarifying the timeline

17:54.500 --> 17:55.340
of the outline.

17:55.780 --> 17:57.459
Can't delete or change it now.

17:58.619 --> 18:00.699
What if... What if

18:00.699 --> 18:01.260
he sees it?

18:03.580 --> 18:05.020
Don't worry about that for now.

18:05.820 --> 18:07.740
Isn't he some hotshot American lawyer?

18:07.859 --> 18:08.820
Probably doesn't have time

18:08.820 --> 18:09.619
to scroll through your Weibo.

18:09.899 --> 18:10.699
Plus, you said

18:10.699 --> 18:11.699
he didn't even recognize you.

18:12.540 --> 18:13.139
But what if...

18:14.139 --> 18:15.060
What if he reads

18:15.060 --> 18:16.580
Chapter 23?

18:16.980 --> 18:17.659
You were the one

18:17.659 --> 18:19.060
who added that wild scene.

18:19.459 --> 18:21.139
No, no, no... I...

18:21.139 --> 18:21.740
I'm gonna...

18:22.619 --> 18:23.780
I'm locking that chapter right now.

18:24.780 --> 18:25.699
Locking it now.

18:27.619 --> 18:28.540
But seriously,

18:28.859 --> 18:29.780
you're dropping the lawsuit

18:29.780 --> 18:30.419
over this little mess?

18:30.899 --> 18:31.459
No!

18:32.260 --> 18:33.139
I'm definitely suing.

18:34.260 --> 18:35.020
I don't believe

18:35.820 --> 18:36.540
Hang City

18:36.699 --> 18:37.980
doesn't have a better law firm.

19:10.859 --> 19:11.699
You two know each other?

19:16.419 --> 19:17.699
No. No, we don't.

19:23.419 --> 19:23.939
No.

19:29.020 --> 19:30.300
Good thing he doesn't remember me.

19:44.340 --> 19:44.939
[These law firms]

19:44.939 --> 19:45.740
[were recommended by a friend.]

19:45.740 --> 19:46.899
[I've already made appointments.]

19:47.020 --> 19:48.340
[You can just go tomorrow.]

19:50.899 --> 19:51.939
[As expected, you're the one]

19:51.939 --> 19:53.060
[I can count on]

19:53.060 --> 19:53.580
[when it counts.]

20:00.179 --> 20:01.300
We know copyright disputes

20:01.300 --> 20:02.820
inside out. You'll win for sure!

20:03.500 --> 20:04.100
So

20:04.100 --> 20:05.179
what's your level as a writer?

20:05.500 --> 20:06.500
How much do you make from a book?

20:08.619 --> 20:09.340
Ms. Ruan,

20:09.340 --> 20:11.060
what Mr. Chen is saying

20:11.060 --> 20:12.300
is that these cases are better

20:12.300 --> 20:13.060
settled out of court.

20:13.419 --> 20:14.939
Mr. Chen means

20:15.540 --> 20:17.060
a PR battle costs a lot.

20:17.740 --> 20:18.980
Mr. Chen...

20:19.139 --> 20:20.619
Follow me right now,

20:20.619 --> 20:21.580
and let's do some

20:21.580 --> 20:22.379
public interactions.

20:22.939 --> 20:23.939
Build up the buzz first.

20:24.899 --> 20:25.859
[Get that so-called Lawyer Zhang]

20:25.859 --> 20:26.740
[out here!]

20:27.260 --> 20:27.780
[All he does]

20:27.780 --> 20:28.780
[is hype things up.]

20:28.980 --> 20:29.699
[Is he a lawyer]

20:29.699 --> 20:30.459
[or an influencer?]

20:30.659 --> 20:31.379
[I'm gonna sue him!]

20:31.619 --> 20:32.820
They sure got it right.

20:33.459 --> 20:34.100
The whole world

20:34.659 --> 20:35.980
is just a giant amateur circus.

20:36.859 --> 20:38.020
[Mr. Fan's definitely not part]

20:38.020 --> 20:39.459
[of some amateur circus act.]

20:39.859 --> 20:42.020
[If Zhikun is the rising star among]

20:42.020 --> 20:43.340
[Hang City's young lawyers,]

20:43.820 --> 20:45.619
[Mr. Fan and Dingzheng are]

20:45.619 --> 20:46.939
[the gold standard for old-school quality.]

20:47.340 --> 20:48.260
[Other than the high fees,]

20:48.260 --> 20:49.419
[no flaws at all.]

20:51.179 --> 20:51.899
Simply put,

20:51.899 --> 20:53.179
this case is about

20:53.179 --> 20:55.020
proving your outline was stolen.

20:55.540 --> 20:57.260
Then can we compare

20:57.260 --> 20:58.780
the wording of both works

20:59.580 --> 21:00.260
to show

21:00.260 --> 21:01.899
they're not

21:01.899 --> 21:03.060
actually similar,

21:03.060 --> 21:04.659
and prove that my work is original

21:04.780 --> 21:05.540
and didn't infringe?

21:06.859 --> 21:08.139
That approach is pretty difficult

21:08.139 --> 21:09.060
right now.

21:09.060 --> 21:10.780
There are indeed many similarities

21:10.780 --> 21:11.540
in the plot.

21:11.820 --> 21:12.580
It might not work in your favor.

21:13.300 --> 21:15.179
Proving the outline was stolen

21:15.179 --> 21:16.859
is the most direct and simplest way.

21:17.740 --> 21:19.020
I understand all that.

21:19.300 --> 21:20.179
But honestly,

21:20.179 --> 21:21.060
the two works just

21:21.060 --> 21:22.100
look a bit similar.

21:22.100 --> 21:23.260
As an original author,

21:23.260 --> 21:24.780
I want the legal recognition.

21:25.619 --> 21:26.540
Miss Ruan, sorry,

21:26.820 --> 21:27.659
but I'm a lawyer,

21:27.980 --> 21:29.020
not your PR team.

21:29.379 --> 21:31.179
I can't support your artistic sentiments.

21:35.659 --> 21:36.139
Understood.

21:42.100 --> 21:42.659
[Miss Ruan,]

21:43.020 --> 21:44.020
[just a friendly heads-up,]

21:44.500 --> 21:45.820
[I don't think any lawyer]

21:45.820 --> 21:46.859
[is gonna go with your approach.]

21:57.219 --> 21:58.300
[How'd it go with Mr. Fan?]

22:02.740 --> 22:04.139
[He heard me out]

22:04.139 --> 22:05.139
[and basically showed me the door.]

22:05.659 --> 22:07.459
[But yeah, going my way]

22:07.459 --> 22:08.820
[would probably be a thankless task.]

22:19.740 --> 22:20.459
Hello, Mr. Liu?

22:21.699 --> 22:22.179
Ruan Yu.

22:23.740 --> 22:25.340
I just called to see

22:25.780 --> 22:26.820
how you're doing with your decision.

22:27.419 --> 22:28.179
[You're really not gonna sue?]

22:29.699 --> 22:30.300
Mr. Liu,

22:31.100 --> 22:32.100
how would you

22:32.340 --> 22:33.139
handle my case

22:33.139 --> 22:34.100
if it were up to you?

22:34.540 --> 22:35.580
Prove the outline was stolen.

22:36.219 --> 22:37.540
That's the simplest way.

22:40.419 --> 22:40.939
What's wrong?

22:41.899 --> 22:43.020
Running into some trouble?

22:43.580 --> 22:44.820
You can tell me.

22:45.300 --> 22:46.740
Even if I'm not your lawyer,

22:47.100 --> 22:48.100
I'm still your friend.

22:50.939 --> 22:51.820
I was wondering

22:52.500 --> 22:54.100
if I could prove

22:54.379 --> 22:55.300
the originality

22:55.300 --> 22:56.020
of my work in this case.

22:56.899 --> 22:58.219
That's actually...

23:04.020 --> 23:04.899
It's okay, Mr. Liu.

23:04.899 --> 23:05.580
I understand.

23:07.179 --> 23:07.659
Yes.

23:09.100 --> 23:09.820
Yes?

23:12.260 --> 23:13.459
Mr. Liu, if you're just doing this

23:13.459 --> 23:14.619
as a friend,

23:15.020 --> 23:15.780
there's no need.

23:16.419 --> 23:17.139
I know...

23:17.219 --> 23:18.179
Of course not.

23:18.179 --> 23:18.939
It's no trouble.

23:20.300 --> 23:21.379
Not at all.

23:25.740 --> 23:27.060
Are you on speaker,

23:27.060 --> 23:27.540
Mr. Liu?

23:28.580 --> 23:28.980
Yeah.

23:29.540 --> 23:30.459
Sorry about that, Ruan Yu.

23:30.699 --> 23:31.459
Hold on a sec.

23:32.340 --> 23:33.459
I need to sign two documents.

23:34.500 --> 23:34.939
Okay.

23:40.780 --> 23:41.820
Any instructions?

23:59.939 --> 24:01.379
Proving your originality

24:01.859 --> 24:03.419
isn't essential evidence,

24:03.899 --> 24:05.020
but as supporting evidence,

24:06.939 --> 24:08.379
it may have a positive impact

24:08.379 --> 24:09.540
on the outcome of the case.

24:09.980 --> 24:12.500
That request can be done.

24:13.699 --> 24:14.820
You're not worried

24:14.820 --> 24:15.939
the comparison won't look good?

24:20.020 --> 24:20.619
Hold on.

24:21.379 --> 24:22.980
Two more documents to sign.

24:25.540 --> 24:25.980
Okay.

24:31.540 --> 24:32.780
In this country, the easiest way

24:32.899 --> 24:33.780
to handle this kind of case

24:34.020 --> 24:36.020
is to go with the stolen outline angle.

24:36.379 --> 24:38.020
Different playbook from

24:38.020 --> 24:38.740
what you're used to overseas.

24:38.740 --> 24:39.740
In any country,

24:39.740 --> 24:41.699
you go with the stolen outline angle.

24:41.699 --> 24:43.100
That's what we've been talking about...

24:45.459 --> 24:46.820
But what if the outline

24:47.379 --> 24:48.619
wasn't stolen at all?

24:48.859 --> 24:49.419
What do you mean?

24:50.899 --> 24:52.139
Mr. Liu, are you still there?

24:52.699 --> 24:54.100
If you're busy,

24:54.419 --> 24:55.939
we can talk later.

24:57.939 --> 24:58.619
Hurry up.

24:58.619 --> 25:00.060
I don't have that many files to sign.

25:10.379 --> 25:12.100
Regardless of how the comparison

25:12.100 --> 25:13.100
turns out,

25:13.500 --> 25:15.419
I think true originality

25:15.939 --> 25:18.100
deserves a shot.

25:19.619 --> 25:20.179
Really?

25:22.179 --> 25:23.379
Thank you so much, Mr. Liu.

25:28.260 --> 25:29.619
No worries. Goodbye.

25:37.659 --> 25:38.859
You can't take this case this way.

25:39.219 --> 25:40.219
You are

25:40.219 --> 25:41.260
pushing it now.

25:42.300 --> 25:43.260
Hang City's full of law firms.

25:43.260 --> 25:44.139
Why do you have to push her

25:44.139 --> 25:45.060
toward Zhikun?

25:46.459 --> 25:47.500
Because I'm the only one

25:47.820 --> 25:49.100
who knows how to handle this case.

25:51.659 --> 25:52.980
You're the only one who knows how?

25:57.740 --> 25:58.859
This isn't about me, is it?

26:02.500 --> 26:04.139
Why go through all this trouble?

26:04.139 --> 26:05.459
You could've just told me.

26:07.699 --> 26:08.859
You know what,

26:10.219 --> 26:10.740
Ruan Yu

26:11.379 --> 26:12.820
is the best of all girls

26:12.820 --> 26:13.780
I've been set up with

26:13.780 --> 26:14.740
over the years.

26:15.980 --> 26:17.939
She's pretty, smart,

26:18.980 --> 26:19.939
and a writer.

26:21.179 --> 26:22.939
I'm a lawyer.

26:24.139 --> 26:25.980
A writer and a lawyer.

26:28.100 --> 26:29.899
That'd make a nice story.

26:31.060 --> 26:31.540
Fine.

26:32.619 --> 26:33.580
I'll wait and see

26:33.580 --> 26:34.980
what episode you end up with her in.

26:35.899 --> 26:36.980
You watch too many dramas.

26:37.780 --> 26:38.619
Dinner tonight?

26:39.020 --> 26:39.419
No.

26:39.699 --> 26:40.459
Where you off to then?

26:42.980 --> 26:43.500
Su City.

26:49.459 --> 26:50.100
Good, don't eat.

26:50.780 --> 26:51.580
Work meeting

26:51.780 --> 26:52.619
turns into a date.

26:59.139 --> 27:00.740
Miss Ruan, see you tonight.

27:05.659 --> 27:06.780
A writer and a lawyer.

27:07.179 --> 27:08.379
That'd make a nice story.

27:10.260 --> 27:10.780
Has a nice ring to it.

27:12.179 --> 27:14.100
Huaisong, you're back?

27:14.580 --> 27:15.859
When did you get back?

27:17.139 --> 27:19.020
Did you come back for that thing?

27:23.219 --> 27:24.139
Fine, I won't ask.

27:25.379 --> 27:27.379
Huaisong, come home for dinner tonight.

27:28.540 --> 27:29.139
I'm eating out.

27:31.260 --> 27:32.459
No. Come on.

27:33.219 --> 27:35.060
Mom really misses you.

27:36.540 --> 27:37.340
I'll pick you up after school.

27:37.740 --> 27:38.859
Go to that place you sent me last time.

27:40.980 --> 27:42.740
Okay. It's a deal.

27:42.820 --> 27:43.980
See you after school.

27:44.100 --> 27:44.619
Love you.

27:51.619 --> 27:52.179
What a coincidence.

27:52.859 --> 27:53.699
Who were you on the phone with?

27:53.699 --> 27:54.340
So happy.

27:54.740 --> 27:55.939
The man who loves me most

27:55.939 --> 27:57.260
in this world.

28:04.500 --> 28:05.340
Give it back!

28:06.060 --> 28:07.500
Put his picture down!

28:10.260 --> 28:11.179
Xu Huaishi,

28:11.580 --> 28:12.100
you're getting

28:12.100 --> 28:13.260
more and more violent.

28:15.459 --> 28:16.820
What, I look at Li Shican for two seconds

28:16.820 --> 28:18.179
and he's gonna get canceled?

28:20.219 --> 28:21.060
Say that again!

28:21.419 --> 28:22.020
Looks like you've got

28:22.020 --> 28:22.980
too much allowance!

28:24.500 --> 28:25.740
My luck

28:25.740 --> 28:26.899
with money is just good.

28:27.580 --> 28:29.500
I just ran out of allowance

28:30.300 --> 28:31.379
and someone's taking me out to eat.

28:33.060 --> 28:33.459
Who?

28:34.100 --> 28:34.980
Huaisong.

28:36.379 --> 28:37.340
A really handsome guy.

28:37.340 --> 28:38.859
Second only to Shican.

28:39.060 --> 28:40.379
Good-looking and rich.

28:40.459 --> 28:43.179
And he spends money on me.

28:53.419 --> 28:53.939
Huaisong!

28:55.939 --> 28:56.740
I'm such a space case.

28:56.939 --> 28:57.740
Gotta go back.

29:04.740 --> 29:05.699
What's Shi doing?

29:07.820 --> 29:08.659
So you're Huaisong?

29:09.580 --> 29:10.699
Don't call her Shi.

29:11.020 --> 29:12.379
Just because you're older doesn't mean

29:12.379 --> 29:14.060
you can take advantage of her.

29:15.459 --> 29:17.379
You're Shi's classmate?

29:18.020 --> 29:19.939
We're buddies.

29:20.459 --> 29:21.300
Not just classmates.

29:21.820 --> 29:22.939
Not just classmates?

29:23.580 --> 29:24.459
Then who are you to her?

29:24.699 --> 29:25.540
What's it to you?

29:27.459 --> 29:29.139
You're trying to pump me

29:29.580 --> 29:30.780
for info about her, aren't you?

29:31.340 --> 29:31.980
No way.

29:33.139 --> 29:34.300
Shi didn't tell you

29:34.619 --> 29:35.379
who I am?

29:35.939 --> 29:36.619
You?

29:38.139 --> 29:39.340
You're that

29:40.379 --> 29:41.300
good-looking, rich guy

29:41.300 --> 29:42.580
who spends money on her,

29:44.340 --> 29:44.820
right?

29:45.340 --> 29:46.179
Shi usually describes me

29:46.179 --> 29:47.100
like that?

29:48.020 --> 29:48.899
It's just money.

29:48.899 --> 29:49.580
Anyone can have it.

29:50.899 --> 29:51.459
Let me tell you,

29:53.859 --> 29:55.459
if you keep messing

29:55.820 --> 29:56.580
with Xu Huaishi,

29:58.659 --> 29:59.580
I won't go easy on you.

29:59.580 --> 29:59.980
Huaisong.

30:02.419 --> 30:03.419
You're still here?

30:05.260 --> 30:06.300
This is my classmate I told you about,

30:06.300 --> 30:07.260
Zhao Yi.

30:07.659 --> 30:08.699
Looks like you've already met.

30:10.179 --> 30:11.260
So you're Zhao Yi?

30:12.139 --> 30:12.939
I've not only met him.

30:13.179 --> 30:14.179
I also know you two

30:14.899 --> 30:16.179
aren't just classmates.

30:19.020 --> 30:19.580
Zhao Yi!

30:22.260 --> 30:24.179
What did you tell Huaisong?

30:25.780 --> 30:29.340
Shouldn't "Huaisong" be his last name?

30:31.379 --> 30:32.500
So I'd be Ms. Shi?

30:32.820 --> 30:35.060
He's Xu Huaisong, my real brother.

30:35.060 --> 30:35.780
Got a problem with that?

30:37.980 --> 30:39.419
No problem. Xu.

30:43.260 --> 30:43.780
Xu.

30:45.540 --> 30:46.580
I've got work tonight.

30:46.659 --> 30:47.459
Not joining you for dinner.

30:54.419 --> 30:54.980
Mr. Liu,

30:54.980 --> 30:55.899
your friend is already here.

30:55.899 --> 30:56.740
I'll show you over.

30:57.020 --> 30:57.580
Okay. Thanks.

31:19.820 --> 31:21.619
Weren't you going to Su City?

31:22.659 --> 31:23.820
Back so soon?

31:33.139 --> 31:35.500
Shouldn't "Huaisong" be his last name?

31:36.100 --> 31:36.939
Is Mr. Liu serious

31:36.939 --> 31:37.659
this time?

31:37.899 --> 31:38.899
That shirt is expensive.

31:39.060 --> 31:40.260
I never saw him wear it.

31:40.820 --> 31:41.540
Who is it?

31:41.820 --> 31:42.780
Do I know this girl?

31:43.500 --> 31:44.580
It's Miss Ruan, the one

31:44.580 --> 31:45.419
with the defamation case.

31:45.699 --> 31:46.899
Mr. Liu drew up the contract this afternoon.

31:47.139 --> 31:47.939
He's securing it tonight.

31:47.980 --> 31:49.179
Securing the deal

31:49.179 --> 31:50.659
or securing the girl?

32:22.659 --> 32:25.260
If I go with Zhikun,

32:25.659 --> 32:26.780
will you be my attorney,

32:26.980 --> 32:28.060
Mr. Liu?

32:31.659 --> 32:32.139
Yes.

32:34.020 --> 32:35.139
So we'll move forward

32:35.139 --> 32:36.340
with the plan we discussed on the phone,

32:36.340 --> 32:36.740
right?

32:37.219 --> 32:37.820
Of course.

32:38.899 --> 32:39.899
We'll provide legal advice

32:39.899 --> 32:40.939
as appropriate.

32:40.939 --> 32:41.580
Never against

32:41.580 --> 32:42.540
the client's wishes.

32:44.939 --> 32:45.459
That's great.

32:45.820 --> 32:47.179
I trust your expertise, Mr. Liu.

32:48.179 --> 32:49.699
Let's sign the contract then.

32:51.740 --> 32:52.500
Now?

32:58.980 --> 32:59.419
No rush.

33:01.780 --> 33:03.260
The contract can wait a few days.

33:04.459 --> 33:05.820
As for the online buzz,

33:06.260 --> 33:07.219
a few days won't matter.

33:07.340 --> 33:08.260
It's not a big deal.

33:09.459 --> 33:10.619
Right, Mr. Liu?

33:10.859 --> 33:12.500
How is it not a big deal?

33:13.020 --> 33:13.459
No.

33:13.459 --> 33:14.379
This can't wait.

33:15.219 --> 33:16.379
The longer the buzz keeps building,

33:16.379 --> 33:17.820
the more risk we take on.

33:18.780 --> 33:19.260
Ruan Yu,

33:19.500 --> 33:20.859
look over the contract carefully.

33:20.859 --> 33:22.139
Ask me if anything's unclear.

33:22.139 --> 33:22.859
No need to be formal.

33:23.219 --> 33:23.820
I've already signed

33:23.820 --> 33:24.780
both copies.

33:25.419 --> 33:25.820
Okay.

33:31.060 --> 33:31.699
I don't have any questions.

33:38.340 --> 33:38.780
Great.

33:40.859 --> 33:41.379
Mr. Liu.

33:42.139 --> 33:42.740
If I file a lawsuit,

33:42.740 --> 33:44.060
what documents do I need to prepare?

33:44.939 --> 33:45.780
The priority

33:46.300 --> 33:47.780
is to get notarized copies

33:47.780 --> 33:49.699
of all the defamatory content

33:49.859 --> 33:50.740
about you online

33:50.740 --> 33:51.980
as soon as possible.

33:52.340 --> 33:53.060
I'll help you with that.

33:53.899 --> 33:55.179
Also, don't let anyone know

33:55.179 --> 33:56.260
you're planning to sue yet,

33:56.379 --> 33:57.500
or you might tip them off.

33:58.060 --> 33:58.740
As for the rest...

33:58.899 --> 33:59.340
Hold on.

34:01.340 --> 34:02.100
Mr. Liu,

34:02.300 --> 34:03.300
aren't you my counsel?

34:04.459 --> 34:05.260
Mr. Xu,

34:06.740 --> 34:07.659
are you involved too?

34:08.899 --> 34:10.219
Mr. Liu handles the court appearances.

34:10.980 --> 34:11.859
I'll help with case prep.

34:15.340 --> 34:17.540
But I can't afford

34:17.540 --> 34:18.380
to pay

34:18.500 --> 34:19.619
two lawyers.

34:20.020 --> 34:20.860
Don't worry about that.

34:21.179 --> 34:22.219
He's just learning.

34:22.219 --> 34:23.179
You don't need to pay him.

34:23.619 --> 34:24.900
Besides, with our connection,

34:25.420 --> 34:26.500
I can give you 20% off.

34:27.380 --> 34:28.299
Thank you, Mr. Liu.

34:31.139 --> 34:31.739
Actually,

34:32.619 --> 34:34.420
I have a few friends in the industry

34:34.420 --> 34:36.060
who've been in copyright disputes.

34:36.619 --> 34:37.699
Mr. Xu, I could refer you to them

34:37.699 --> 34:38.900
if you want to study.

34:40.619 --> 34:41.619
I don't mind.

34:45.219 --> 34:46.219
Mr. Liu, is that okay with you?

35:00.659 --> 35:02.020
After all, this isn't

35:02.020 --> 35:03.139
a Zhikun case.

35:03.659 --> 35:04.460
So if Mr. Xu

35:04.460 --> 35:05.420
gets involved,

35:05.420 --> 35:08.219
it might not look great for the firm,

35:12.339 --> 35:12.860
right?

35:18.860 --> 35:19.460
Mr. Xu,

35:20.460 --> 35:20.980
when you say

35:20.980 --> 35:22.420
"help with case prep,"

35:23.940 --> 35:25.500
does that mean you'll advise

35:25.860 --> 35:26.819
Mr. Liu on strategy,

35:27.380 --> 35:28.779
but not handle everything...

35:28.779 --> 35:29.860
The first step of case prep

35:30.819 --> 35:32.179
is fully understanding the case.

35:33.259 --> 35:34.339
So you have to

35:34.339 --> 35:35.060
review all the documents?

35:35.460 --> 35:36.860
Including the entire novel?

35:39.139 --> 35:40.380
Miss Ruan, is there something

35:41.580 --> 35:42.460
in your novel

35:42.460 --> 35:43.339
you'd rather not share?

35:46.659 --> 35:47.580
No, no.

35:50.060 --> 35:50.580
No.

35:52.500 --> 35:54.100
Alright. Contract's signed.

35:54.580 --> 35:56.339
Let me set up a work group chat.

35:56.860 --> 35:58.339
That way we can communicate easily.

35:58.860 --> 35:59.339
Alright?

36:00.659 --> 36:02.100
Sure.

36:10.619 --> 36:11.819
In 1,000 meters,

36:11.940 --> 36:13.580
you'll get on the airport expressway.

37:02.219 --> 37:03.020
[Mr. Xu will handle]

37:03.020 --> 37:04.420
[organizing the plot points]

37:04.420 --> 37:05.420
[from the novel for our case.]

37:05.739 --> 37:06.380
[If you have any questions,]

37:07.139 --> 37:07.900
[feel free to reach out to him.]

37:14.219 --> 37:14.940
[Mr. Liu,]

37:14.980 --> 37:16.420
[for the plot organization part,]

37:16.540 --> 37:17.179
[can I just]

37:17.179 --> 37:17.940
[coordinate with you?]

37:20.460 --> 37:22.100
[Mr. Xu has more experience]

37:22.100 --> 37:23.100
[with plagiarism checks.]

37:28.819 --> 37:29.860
[I just thought with Mr. Xu]

37:29.860 --> 37:30.900
[being overseas, the time difference]

37:30.980 --> 37:31.659
[would be a hassle.]

37:32.219 --> 37:34.100
[Plus, he's probably pretty busy.]

37:35.060 --> 37:36.219
[Don't worry about the time difference.]

37:36.580 --> 37:37.460
[He's a night owl.]

37:38.060 --> 37:39.139
[And no matter how busy he is,]

37:39.619 --> 37:41.060
[for my sake,]

37:41.299 --> 37:42.460
[he'll make time for this case.]

37:43.179 --> 37:44.219
[Once the materials are organized,]

37:44.219 --> 37:45.179
[you can post them in the group chat.]

38:07.819 --> 38:08.380
Hello?

38:11.299 --> 38:11.900
Man,

38:12.779 --> 38:13.980
this type of case

38:13.980 --> 38:15.619
is your specialty, right?

38:16.020 --> 38:18.020
You told me to say in the group chat

38:18.020 --> 38:19.500
that you're handling this case.

38:19.500 --> 38:20.460
I did it.

38:20.540 --> 38:22.380
Then Ruan Yu responded,

38:22.380 --> 38:23.460
and you just went silent.

38:24.779 --> 38:25.619
What's your deal?

38:26.179 --> 38:26.860
You're putting me

38:26.860 --> 38:28.219
in a really tough spot here.

38:35.819 --> 38:36.860
If you're really that uncomfortable

38:36.860 --> 38:38.580
being in the middle,

38:39.259 --> 38:39.980
just come sit over here.

38:43.020 --> 38:43.540
Fine.

38:48.900 --> 38:49.540
You can have her

38:49.540 --> 38:50.659
add me on WeChat.

38:51.580 --> 38:52.659
I see now.

38:53.339 --> 38:55.060
You came back all of a sudden

38:55.179 --> 38:56.339
for Ruan Yu.

38:58.779 --> 38:59.779
Shi got into some trouble.

39:00.540 --> 39:01.420
That's a terrible excuse.

39:02.060 --> 39:02.819
Seriously?

39:03.739 --> 39:05.179
If you have time to gossip,

39:05.460 --> 39:06.380
why not just have the client

39:06.380 --> 39:07.259
contact me?

39:07.940 --> 39:08.699
Wait.

39:09.500 --> 39:10.659
Why do you want her

39:10.659 --> 39:11.219
to contact you?

39:13.779 --> 39:15.060
Don't tell me you added her

39:15.460 --> 39:16.940
and she didn't accept?

39:16.940 --> 39:17.860
Nonsense.

39:19.580 --> 39:20.460
So I guessed right!

39:24.619 --> 39:26.179
Looks like you've got more experience

39:26.940 --> 39:28.339
being rejected than I do, Mr. Liu.

39:31.100 --> 39:31.779
You got anything or not?

39:31.779 --> 39:32.460
If not, I'm hanging up.

39:34.179 --> 39:35.100
I'll hang up first.

39:40.179 --> 39:41.380
I've got more experience?

40:21.980 --> 40:23.100
[Here's the defamation record]

40:23.100 --> 40:23.819
[I've organized so far.]

40:24.219 --> 40:25.900
[I already had it notarized]

40:25.900 --> 40:26.980
[at the notary office this morning.]

40:27.619 --> 40:28.940
[Please take a look and let me know]

40:28.940 --> 40:30.060
[if anything else needs to be added.]

40:41.219 --> 40:42.699
[You should add him on WeChat.]

40:42.699 --> 40:43.860
[He's in too many work group chats.]

40:43.860 --> 40:45.060
[Might miss things sometimes.]

40:52.100 --> 40:53.900
Add Xu Huaisong on WeChat?

41:11.259 --> 41:13.219
4308.

41:34.980 --> 41:36.420
[Back then, I spent three years]

41:36.420 --> 41:37.619
[going over his info]

41:37.980 --> 41:39.380
[and never found a reason to add him.]

41:40.299 --> 41:42.420
[Ten years later, here it is.]

41:44.219 --> 41:44.900
[Life really has]

41:44.900 --> 41:46.100
[a twisted sense of humor.]

41:57.540 --> 41:58.540
What do I say?

42:00.699 --> 42:02.380
Hello, Mr. Xu.

42:02.980 --> 42:03.659
This is Ruan Yu.

42:05.339 --> 42:07.420
No. Too formal.

42:21.739 --> 42:22.380
No.

42:23.219 --> 42:24.339
Too stiff.

42:30.219 --> 42:31.420
What do I do?

42:33.020 --> 42:34.819
No! I can't add him!

42:35.940 --> 42:37.540
Talking to him about the novel

42:37.540 --> 42:38.500
feels too awkward

42:38.779 --> 42:39.819
What if I slip up?

43:08.060 --> 43:09.699
[A young lady with no legal background]

43:09.699 --> 43:11.500
[would rather figure out]

43:11.500 --> 43:13.100
[notarization herself]

43:13.380 --> 43:14.219
[than let you help.]

43:14.540 --> 43:15.380
[Looks like she really doesn't]

43:15.380 --> 43:16.259
[want to deal with you.]

43:26.100 --> 43:28.500
How... Did I just add him?

43:29.100 --> 43:29.619
What...

43:30.259 --> 43:31.540
What did my friend request

43:31.540 --> 43:32.259
say?

44:00.460 --> 44:00.940
Have a seat.

44:05.980 --> 44:06.900
One more thing.

44:07.460 --> 44:08.580
Someone

44:09.139 --> 44:10.699
found a phone in the auditorium.

44:11.699 --> 44:13.619
Is anyone here to claim it?

44:17.179 --> 44:17.940
Nobody?

44:21.299 --> 44:22.100
Whose phone is this?

44:27.500 --> 44:28.500
The "study or marry me"

44:28.980 --> 44:30.259
person,

44:31.139 --> 44:31.739
come up

44:31.739 --> 44:32.940
and get your phone.

44:39.540 --> 44:40.219
Whose phone?

44:43.980 --> 44:45.380
Sir. Sir.

44:45.460 --> 44:46.100
Sir, I'm sorry.

44:46.860 --> 44:47.500
It's mine.

44:47.980 --> 44:48.540
Don't bring

44:48.540 --> 44:49.779
your phone to school anymore.

44:50.940 --> 44:51.940
Focus on your studies.

44:53.420 --> 44:54.500
Thank you, sir. Sorry about that.
